fields.title: placement_pass
fields.description: When the feature should be placed relative to others. Earlier passes in the list are guaranteed to occur before later passes. Order is not guaranteed within each pass.

fields.title: minecraft:biome_filter
fields.description: List of filter tests to determine which biomes this rule will attach to.

subForm.title: Biome Filter
subForm.description: Filters allow data objects to specify test criteria which allows their use. Filters can be defined by a single object of type (Filter Test), an array of tests, collection groups, or a combination of these objects.
